    "created_at": "2015-07-17T21:09:33Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-17T21:09:33Z",
    "body": "I did the socket/pipe thing and it works great, except on Windows I would need to pass on the foreground activation love ([details here](http://blogs.msdn.com/b/oldnewthing/archive/2009/02/20/9435239.aspx)) by calling [AllowSetForegroundWindow](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/desktop/ms632668) which is where now suddenly I have to do native things. I have not found any way of doing this with node.js short of writing a native module. Any chance we could have support for foreground activation love?\n"
